EXTRACTED VALUE: Scene It?'s brand of movie trivia is one that will be enjoyed by both casual and hardcore movie fans.
Legions is incredibly fun, but the serious lack of modes will end your experience far too early.
Origins won't win over staunchly anti-RPG players, but for fans of the genre, this is quite a deal.
DDR Universe offers the standard sorts of changes and upgrades you'd expect from this nearly decade-old series.
New multiplayer additions make this the best Lost Planet experience so far, but there's not enough here to warrant another purchase for veterans.
MX vs. ATV Untamed is a fun off-road racing game that will tide you over until the next racer comes out, which looks like it could be a while.
It really shows that EA not only took notes from the films and books, but listened to the fans to give them what they want.
